title: Hour 2 - Brady & Rodgers Underperforming, LaVar Arrington
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Brady & Rodgers Underperforming, LaVar Arrington
description:
Dan and the Danettes try to figure out what the problems are for Aaron Rodgers and Tom Brady. And "2 Pros & a Cup of Joe" radio host, "Up on Game" podcast host, and former NFL stud, LaVar Arrington stops by to weigh in on the latest NFL action.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
